nodes.text: Mynock mud pies were a dish made with mynocks, a non-sentient species. They were sold at the concession areas of Aucellis Park, which was located on the moon Keriba VI. Despite being closed, the areas were fully stocked with foods such as Mynock mud pie and Nerf burgers.
Mynock mud pies were mentioned in "Beneath Aucellis Park," a Star Wars Roleplaying Game mini-adventure authored by Morrie Mullins and published on the Wizards of the Coast website on August 21, 2003.
